metadata.name: Flow of time
metadata.description:
Time flows like a river  
Time flows in you  
Time flows as the wind blows  
Fluttering butterflies and singing birds  
The beauty of nature cannot be described in words  
Take your time and heal yourself  
Nature is the portal to the inner self  
There are far better things ahead than any we leave behind  
There's no such thing as a perfect time...  
Every moment is precious  
Before time flies and leaves us in emptiness  
Cherish your time in happiness.
